il.technion.ewolf.kbr.openkad

クラス KadNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • il.technion.ewolf.kbr.openkad.KadNode
  • 直系の既知のサブクラス:
    UndeadKadNode

    public class KadNode
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper for Node type. Used to keep track on the following: 1. last contact time - the most recent time a message was received from this node 2. being ping - expecting a ping to be received from this node

      • lockForPing

        public boolean lockForPing()
        Signals this node is being pinged. Important: If true is returned, you must call releasePingLock to allow this node to be pinged in the future
        戻り値:
        true if the node was not being pinged, false if it was already locked
